                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "line_text": "Où j'attendrais l'heure de ton réveil.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "Dors, calme et douce et que rien ne dérange,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Le songe heureux qui berce ton sommeil !",
